Title: Monitor Pure Storage FlashArrays
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1688383212
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.3.0b1

This Werk adds services monitoring <i>"Pure Storage FlashArrays"</i>.
Configuring a special agent by the same name lets you monitor the devices using the plugins

LI: <i>Pure Storage FlashArray: Ethernet Port</i>
LI: <i>Pure Storage FlashArray: Internal Alerts</i>
LI: <i>Pure Storage FlashArray: Overall Capacity</i>
LI: <i>Pure Storage FlashArray: Volume Capacity</i>
LI: <i>Pure Storage FlashArray: Fibre Channel Port</i>
LI: <i>Pure Storage FlashArray: InfiniBand Port</i>
LI: <i>Pure Storage FlashArray: Storage Bay</i>
LI: <i>Pure Storage FlashArray: Fan</i>

For details please refer to the corresponding plugin manpages.
